msgstr "Ofte Stillede Spørgsmål"

msgid "How far in advance should I book?"
msgstr "Hvor lang tid i forvejen bør jeg booke?"

msgid "We recommend booking at least 24 hours in advance for best availability. However, we do accept same-day bookings depending on our current schedule. Contact us directly for urgent bookings."
msgstr "Vi anbefaler at booke mindst 24 timer i forvejen. Vi accepterer dog dagsbestillinger afhængigt af vores aktuelle skema. Kontakt os direkte for akutte bestillinger."

msgid "What payment methods do you accept?"
msgstr "Hvilke betalingsmetoder accepterer I?"

msgid "We accept all major credit cards, debit cards, and bank transfers. Online payment is processed securely through our booking system. You can also pay directly to the driver if pre-arranged."
msgstr "Vi accepterer alle større kredit- og debetkort samt bankoverførsler. Online betaling behandles sikkert via vores bookingsystem. Du kan også betale direkte til chauffør, hvis det er aftalt på forhånd."

msgid "What if I need to cancel my booking?"
msgstr "Hvad sker der, hvis jeg skal afbestille?"

msgid "Cancellations made 24 hours or more in advance receive a full refund. Cancellations within 24 hours may incur a cancellation fee. Please contact us immediately if you need to modify your booking."
msgstr "Afbestillinger foretaget 24 timer eller mere i forvejen modtager fuld refusion. Afbestillinger inden for 24 timer kan medføre et afbestillingsgebyr. Kontakt os straks, hvis du skal ændre din bestilling."

msgid "Are your vehicles wheelchair accessible?"
msgstr "Er jeres køretøjer tilgængelige for kørestolsbrugere?"

msgid "Yes, we have wheelchair accessible vehicles available. Please mention your accessibility requirements when booking so we can arrange the appropriate vehicle for your needs."
msgstr "Ja, vi har kørestolsvenlige køretøjer. Angiv venligst dine tilgængelighedskrav ved booking, så vi kan arrangere det rette køretøj."

msgid "Can I bring luggage and how much is included?"
msgstr "Kan jeg medbringe bagage og hvor meget er inkluderet?"

msgid "Absolutely! All our vehicles have spacious boot space to accommodate standard luggage. Oversized baggage may require a larger vehicle. Our team will assist with luggage handling as part of our service."
msgstr "Absolut! Alle vores køretøjer har rummelig bagageplads til standardbagage. Oversized bagage kan kræve et større køretøj. Vores team hjælper med bagagehåndtering som en del af vores service."

msgid "Ready to Book Your Transfer?"
msgstr "Klar til at Booke din Transfer?"

msgid "Experience premium airport transfer service today."
msgstr "Oplev premium lufthavnstransfer service i dag."
